org.cs2c.nginlib.config
接口 Element

所有超级接口：
java.lang.Cloneable
所有已知子接口：
Block, Directive
public interface Element
extends java.lang.Cloneable

作者：
Mikes

Element represents a part of nginx's configuration file. There are two kinds of Element: Block and Directive.

For the following configure fregement:
upstream real_server {
server 10.1.60.8:8080;
}

The upsream is a Block, representing a range of directive. The server is a directive with end of ";".

另请参见：
Block, Directive
